Hey all — one late night I decided to record a session of me updating third-party modules with mypy types.

I hope you find it helpful! Very happy to create more videos like this on commonly held questions about mypy and other things Python! My goal is for everyone to be an expert on this :slightly_smiling_face: https://instabase.workplace.com/groups/352991735359942/permalink/399604720698643/
I’ve memorialized the link here in the Engineering Resources page: https://instabase.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/IB/pages/13729813/Engineering+Resources

Please add to other docs where it might be relevant
